OL,3,CFinance Minister refuses to rule out
OL,4,Crecommending rates rise
OL,6,FStormont's Finance Minister has
OL,7,Frefused to rule out recommending a
OL,8,Frates rise to the Executive when it
OL,9,Fmeets later this week.
OL,11,FCaoimhe Archibald is due to hold talks
OL,12,Fwith the Treasury on Wednesday about
OL,13,Fthe government's 3 and a half billion
OL,14,Fpounds package offered to the incoming
OL,15,FExecutive.
OL,17,FThe Sinn Fein minister has said she
OL,18,Fwill be pressing for substantive
OL,19,Fengagement on implementing a new
OL,20,Ffiscal framework for Northern Ireland
OL,21,Fduring a meeting with the Treasury.
