OL,6,FThe Government has said the
OL,7,Fpowersharing Executive should raise
OL,8,F#113 million in additional funds over
OL,9,Fthe next year and produce a plan to
OL,10,Fdeliver sustainable finances as a
OL,11,Fcondition for the Treasury writing off
OL,12,Falmost #600 million of Stormont debt.
OL,14,FBut Stormont leaders have voiced
OL,15,Fconcern about introducing new revenue-
OL,16,Fraising measures in the region and
OL,17,Fhave ruled out increasing the regional
OL,18,Frate in Northern Ireland by 15% to
OL,19,Fraise the #113 million.
