OL,6,F"The Executive does do revenue
OL,7,Fraising" the MLA for East Londonderry
OL,8,Fsaid "the starting point is that we
OL,9,Fneed to be properly funded in the
OL,10,Ffirst place so that departments and
OL,11,Fministers are able to plan about how
OL,12,Fthey are able to deliver their public
OL,13,Fservices."J"We have a very challenging
OL,14,Fbudgetary situation. And we are going
OL,15,Fto have to prioritise and make
OL,16,Fdecisions."
