OL,6,FWhen pressed on if she would be
OL,7,Frecommending a rates increase to the
OL,8,FExecutive, the Minister said she did
OL,9,Fnot want to preempt the discussion
OL,10,Fwith her Executive colleagues that she
OL,11,Fwas aiming to have later this week.
OL,13,F"There is a very difficult balance to
OL,14,Fstrike.
OL,16,F"We do want to be able to deliver high
OL,17,Fquality public services. People
OL,18,Frightly expect that they will have
OL,19,Fhave access to high quality public
OL,20,Fservices.
