OL,6,FDuring this session, Ms Archibald
OL,7,Fsaid: "I have written to the Chief
OL,8,FSecretary to the Treasury setting out
OL,9,Fmy significant concerns in relation to
OL,10,Felements of the financial package,
OL,11,Fincluding the stipulations on revenue
OL,12,Fraising.
OL,14,F"I am meeting with the Chief Secretary
OL,15,Fto the Treasury tomorrow where I will
OL,16,Fbe pressing for substantive engagement
OL,17,Fon how we develop and implement a new
OL,18,Ffiscal framework.
